title: Russian travelers say they fear one question: ‘Where are you from?’
description: CNBC Travel spoke with Russians about how traveling has changed for them — including how they've been treated — since the outbreak of the war in Ukraine.

title: The top 3 countries where it’s easy to settle into a new life abroad, according to expats
